    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives super smoothly and is totally ready for some new adventures with a new owner! If you're looking for a reliable, great-looking car that's ready to hit the road today, you've found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
