    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.8L flat-six M97 powerplant paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated engine provides a linear power band and an evocative exhaust note, while the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) ensures the chassis remains composed through high-load cornering. It sits on 19-inch 'Lobster Fork' alloys and maintains excellent mechanical integrity, with a recently serviced cooling system and inspected IMS. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight and the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern electric systems lack. A mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the open road.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
