    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is the epitome of reliable luxury, presented in a striking Obsidian Black that still retains a deep, mirror-like shine. While you might find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia from careful highway use, the body remains straight and free of any significant blemishes. Step inside to a serene Parchment leather cabin that has been meticulously kept; the seats are supple with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side, and the genuine wood trim remains vibrant and scratch-free. Mechanically, this vehicle is in great shape, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with a recent full-synthetic oil service and a multi-point inspection. The V6 engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the cabin remains whisper-quiet at highway speeds. It sits on a set of premium all-season tires with approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a plush ride from day one. This is a well-loved, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
